org.jaudiotagger.tag.id3

Class ID3v24Frames

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jaudiotagger.tag.datatype.AbstractValuePair<String,String>
      • org.jaudiotagger.tag.datatype.AbstractStringStringValuePair
        • org.jaudiotagger.tag.id3.ID3Frames
          • org.jaudiotagger.tag.id3.ID3v24Frames

  • public class ID3v24Frames
extends ID3Frames
    Defines ID3v24 frames and collections that categorise frames.

    You can include frames here that are not officially supported as long as they can be used within an ID3v24Tag

    Version:
    $Id: ID3v24Frames.java 1059 2012-07-04 12:18:35Z paultaylor $
